<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Food Insecurity Information</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa 0%, #e3f2fd 100%);
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto 0 auto;
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.10);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #1a73e8;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #1565c0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        }
        .section p, .section ul {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .section ul {
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
        }
        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a73e8 0%, #34a853 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.08);
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .back-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1565c0 0%, #2e7d32 100%);
        }
        .logo {
            position: fixed;
            top: 30px;
            right: 40px;
            width: 90px;
            height: 90px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.15);
            background: white;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px 8px 0 8px;
                padding: 1.2rem 0.5rem;
            }
            .logo {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                top: 10px;
                right: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Hunger Stoppers Logo" class="logo">
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-button">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
        <h1>Understanding Food Insecurity</h1>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>What is Food Insecurity?</h2>
            <p>Food insecurity is the lack of consistent access to enough food for an active, healthy life. It can affect anyone, regardless of their background or circumstances.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Key Facts</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Millions of people worldwide face food insecurity daily</li>
                <li>Food insecurity can lead to serious health problems</li>
                <li>Children are particularly vulnerable to the effects of food insecurity</li>
                <li>Food insecurity can affect mental and physical development</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>How You Can Help</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Donate to local food banks</li>
                <li>Volunteer at community food programs</li>
                <li>Support organizations fighting food insecurity</li>
                <li>Raise awareness about the issue</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 